EPS32
    D4 = dht input
    D13 = LED output to relay module
    D26 = water pump output to relay module
    D27 = fan output to relay module
    D34 (ADC1 CH6) = LDR input (considerar adc < 20 para acionar led, usando r=220)
    D35 (ADC1 CH7) = soil moisture sensor 



RELAY
    COM = negative
    in1 = lighting (no)
    in2 = fan (no)
    in3 = pump (no)